## 1.7.0
  * Add bidirectional chat between orchestrator and user via dashboard
  * New MCP tools: kanban_chat, kanban_chat_poll
  * kanban_chat with wait_for_response blocks until user answers in the browser
  * Floating chat bubble with browser notifications when input is needed
  * FIFO question queue — multiple questions answered in order
  * Free-form messaging — user can send messages anytime, picked up via kanban_check_signals
  * Optimistic message rendering on send
  * 500ms chat polling for responsive UX

## 1.5.0
  * Mobile responsive layout (< 768px breakpoint)
    * Compact stacked header with relocated elapsed timer
    * Horizontally scrollable agent bar
    * Swipeable tab-based column navigation (BLK/RDY/WIP/DONE)
    * Always-visible card action buttons for touch devices
    * Log panel as floating action button + bottom sheet overlay
    * Full-screen task detail and diff modals
    * Unified diff renderer (replaces side-by-side on mobile)
    * Collapsible file dropdown in diff modal (replaces sidebar)
  * Add left/right navigation arrows to task detail modal for browsing tasks by ID

